These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, asparagus, blueberry, garlic
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, lizard, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, ice-hockey, climbing, baseball
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the owner of the cat##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the far left##1
4. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the ferret is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person eating asparagus##2
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the owner of the lizard##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | blueberry | garlic  | asparagus | artichoke  |
| Pet         | turtle    | ferret  | cat       | lizard     |
| Sport   | climbing     | skiing | baseball       | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, drawing, magic-tricks, reading
House: craftsman, colonial, farmhouse, townhouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, surfing, swimming
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is between the townhouse house and the person who's hobby is reading##2
5. the townhouse house is the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
7. the farmhouse house is the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | drawing | chess    | reading  | magic-tricks |
| House   | townhouse  | craftsman  | colonial   | farmhouse    |
| Sport         | sailing | swimming | climbing | surfing      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, sprite, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, gardening, photography
House: modern, townhouse, palace, wooden
1. the townhouse house is between the wooden house and the person drinking mirinda##2
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the modern house##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
6. the modern house is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the palace house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | tea         | lemonade   | sprite    |
| Hobby         | cooking | photography | collecting | gardening |
| House   | palace   | townhouse        | wooden      | modern   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, dutch, german, polish
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, brown, fuchsia, chestnut
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the ship and the polish##2
3. the german is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
5. the german is on the right of the australian##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person who likes emerald and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | polish        | dutch   | australian | german |
| Color         | fuchsia | emerald | brown    | chestnut |
| Transport     | scooter       | bus     | ship       | car    |

