.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, papaya, pepper, pomegranate
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, jazz, hip-hop, rock
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cycling, handball, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is the fan of jazz##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the fan of country##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
4. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person eating papaya is between the fan of jazz and the fan of hip-hop##2
7. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | pepper  | papaya    | pomegranate | lettuce  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | rock       | jazz        | country    |
| Sport         | cycling | badminton | volleyball  | handball |

