.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, mango, pepper, tomato
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, photography, woodworking, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, parkour, rugby
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is the person eating eggplant##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person eating mango##1
5. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | tomato  | eggplant    | pepper | mango       |
| Hobby         | writing | photography | chess  | woodworking |
| Sport   | parkour   | rugby      | handball  | cricket     |

