.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, garlic, raspberry, strawberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, puzzles, reading
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, almond-milk, juice
1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating garlic##1
3. the person drinking coffee is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person drinking coffee and the person eating strawberry##2
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person drinking juice##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person drinking cola##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | strawberry  | raspberry | eggplant | garlic     |
| Hobby   | board-games | puzzles   | reading  | camping    |
| Beverage     | cola        | juice       | coffee      | almond-milk |

