2. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person who growspoppy is the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
6. the person who growssunflower is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Flower   | poppy | sunflower  | balloon-flower       | daisy   |
| Hobby      | drawing     | hiking | filmmaking | reading |
| Pet        | pony        | rabbit | ferret     | hamster |

