2. the person who growsorchid is the mechanic##1
3. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the dancer##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is between the person watching romance movies and the mechanic##2
6. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
7. the person who growsbegonia is the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
